The whole solution can be found [here][1].

Where&#39;s what&#39;s causing the issue, taken from the above link:


&gt; cli will copy files with json extension to resource dir, in Android&#39;s
&gt; case, android/app/build/res.
&gt; 
&gt; Here comes a problem. If package.json at the project root gets copied,
&gt; it won&#39;t be renamed as other package.json in node_modules (e.g.
&gt; raw/node_modules_reactnativecodepush_package.json). Instead, it will
